msgid ""
"Added a new ``unique`` choice to the ``[libvirt]/sysinfo_serial`` "
"configuration which if set will result in the guest serial number being set "
"to ``instance.uuid``. This is now the default value of the ``[libvirt]/"
"sysinfo_serial`` config option and is the recommended choice since it "
"ensures the guest serial is the same even if the instance is migrated "
"between hosts."
