"``AggregateDiskFilter`` are now deprecated. They will be removed in a future "
"release and should no longer be used. Their functionality has been replaced "
"with a placement native approach by combining host aggregate mirroring added "
"in Rocky and initial allocation ratios added in Stein. See the `scheduler "
"documentation`_ for details."
